MongoDB Connection String (optional, defaults to mongodb://localhost:27017/)

Use the line below if your MongoDB requires authentication or is on a different host/port

MONGO_URI=mongodb://your_user:your_password@your_host:your_port/

Use this line for default local MongoDB without authentication

MONGO_URI=mongodb://localhost:27017

JWT Secret Key (IMPORTANT: Change this for production!)

Generate using: openssl rand -hex 32

SECRET_KEY=change_this_very_secret_key_in_production_32_bytes_long